title: NO-FEE Modern 1 Bed 1 Bath in Hudson Yards!
posting_body: ['Sabrina Rosal', 'Phone: 201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>', 'This no-fee, beautiful 1 bed 1 bath offers condo-level finishes, a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a spa-like bathroom with Italian porcelain tiling, oak wood flooring, chrome fixtures, oversized windows, individually controlled heat & air, and an in-home washer & dryer.', 'This luxury building offers a 24-hour doorman, expansive solarium and sky lounge with private cabanas, squash court, fitness center, co-working spaces, golf simulator, pet washing room, bike & resident storage, valet services, and Caffe Vento on site.', 'Conveniently located near the 7/A/C/E/ W 39th St Ferry.', 'Note: Listed rent is net effective based on 1 month free.', 'Gross rent is $5,790.', 'LISTING #138517', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Health Club', 'Subway', 'Laundry', 'Bicycle Room', 'Storage', 'Roof Deck', 'Wheelchair Access', 'Receiving Room', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Dishwasher', 'Hardwood', 'Light', 'NO FEE', 'Laundry In Unit', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Sabrina Rosal', 'Phone: 201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>', 'To view, call or text Sabrina Rosal at:', '201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>']
